headline.main: Real Madrid Thrash Eibar Without Bale and Ronaldo
headline.print_headline: Real Madrid Thrash Eibar Without Bale and Ronaldo

lead_paragraph: Real Madrid overcame the absence of Gareth Bale and Cristiano Ronaldo to romp to a 4-1 win at tiny Eibar on Saturday and provisionally return to the top of La Liga.
